<div class="theorem" id="theorem-OSLI" acro="OSLI" titletext="Orthogonal Sets are Linearly Independent">
<h5 class="theorem">
<span class="type">Theorem </span><span class="acro">OSLI</span><span class="titletext"> Orthogonal Sets are Linearly Independent</span>
</h5>
<div class="statement"><p>Suppose that $S$ is an orthogonal set of nonzero vectors.  Then $S$ is linearly independent.</p></div>
<div class="proof"><a knowl="./knowls/proof.OSLI.knowl">Proof</a></div>
